
# Grouper Release Instructions

Instructions for preparing a Grouper release.

$Id: .RELEASE_INSTRUCTIONS,v 1.4 2006-06-19 17:00:57 blair Exp $

---

## To Prepare For A Release:

* Update *serialVersionUID* as appropriate
* Test CVS
  * OSX/HSQLDB
  * OSX/Postgres
  * Solaris/HSQLDB
  * Solaris/Oracle
  * `contrib/cdg`
* Document
  * `doc/NEWS`, including version number and release date
* Update `impl.version` in `build.xml`
* Tag, branch and tarball

    % cvs tag GROUPER_$MAJOR_$MINOR_[PATCH]
    % cvs up -A
    % cd $ELSEWHERE
    % cvs co -r$TAG grouper
    % cvs tag -b GROUPER_$MAJOR_$MINOR_BRANCH
    % cvs export -r $TAG -d ./grouper-api-$VERSION grouper
    % changelog > grouper-api-$VERSION/doc/CHANGES
    % ant html
    % mv dist/api grouper-api-$VERSION/doc/javadoc
    % tar czvf ./grouper-api-$VERSION.tgz ./grouper-$VERSION

* Test tarball
  * OSX/HSQLDB
  * OSX/Postgres
  * Solaris/HSQLDB
  * Solaris/Oracle
  * `contrib/cdg`
* Pass along tarball
* Notify grouper-dev

